: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;瓦数增加&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;"&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 24px 0 0; text-align: center; font-size: 32px;"&gt; 1,162&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; 2025 年美国可再生能源&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/tNQEVQWsxEB3qhW4Yn-771Nb5UeGpzjWaJ1j1-ytt4FzhShyH26nX3HSoMiAwMDka2cR8Eo6d5ant5zWOpA1OIZ1IjhkbJxW6koXsud7ifmyLVq8ikERbNMIs85OrfP_Z6S6-DDrgP_LvX7htojDgOLU9KtuYz-J32PHkS-aBgOjz24yPSqSkwqoBVo8d4yt1dNQeD8ZC5FCvnrnma_l2d6mWAqYFvze3CcuPc5oUc3W6-b00Weq38Q7V3T-HErs5wjfswsktQoPpagfGSBGRqchlPqeI5xLkggcW0P4vi11i8GWg3UsTo_MkSNC4jG6DrMhh_WSL7ENvKdNNm51pS7L42OI98F3eZTjXHFWeNr6z6dE_Reyna5HIZGd4YiR--hNXOGosxmLjBSn8SqCGt7qfC3H1ExPkowotN0z_D-I_NxoMwfOvHAtZ7jP2C0WYFhY6F4iJtzyQpgKvNweAF5qygyKo5wdzWAc0t5FuhgSDT97ZrnBrsGOf9sS9nlukRimxiyFeaoi3fpWzvBpB1QfoBRtXr-kGzMWF76SRIWX/peYtN1NcfbcCeKM36CCOQr19oShsWq6K/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="可再生能源无视特朗普的攻击，创下新纪录"&gt;发电&lt;/a&gt;量将比上年增长 10%。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;大家都在说话&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;"&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-size: 22px; margin: 0;"&gt; “在全国范围内谈论它并成为一个竞选问题，这&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/TrfrQOUQq5TZH1TWyKOWdXo0D3W9aa1zE-vay87r-q2RXgs8FFd4LtqmnFQizOvMaZb9inZOlJpy-hJpgz25RgeaUAw4uoEmJU1uKTHc72SUnBs9Kz00GEEp8y3tBWlp9t8V4DAs__5_TrxYFjhRSDeb3SwFLYDxft96MpDmPoQKgAkRwpXK17gVRWCge9X7znFkG_N0Djp9z3TulKxDsJl5jJlAZBahhEo7q_5DFbrQtqPYibCv8kqj4uVYjkSAnWcBatyUHA-zKq1ncJC-3HXdRwVFXFp0JNry7xPwUxV4r0ABWKznCr2GZ3YHNe0MIL2CPktPPkoAev3fwKLPLjhUCAVCMEG-Fo6koV_NxT6ZF3wIgLgD-qk6ca5UtbU2OCrRN5Z6zT6s4FcWgSdj2dnL1mWzRJKNCWBVKrY2kiJCpmBOPMujbtGS6ZN10S4BlkzOoPfF7snkIlY1bUXCnWE4-DoxtP2aiiErPfN8z4Oxhw/edUzTaNmrCMgaGvDPGLag33BXz5lWpEK/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: inherit;" target="_blank" title="飙升的电费在中期选举前激起选民的愤怒"&gt;在现代历史上是完全前所未有的&lt;/a&gt;。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-weight: 700; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;约书亚·巴塞切斯&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; margin: 0;"&gt;杜兰大学教授&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; line-height: 140%; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;主题？当然，这将导致电费飙升。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;本周零&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ifpi6anCKrei2kFFP66Dxf7mJmdk2iFW5xhV1PLUZw1WGRnvjikdH1yigITs4BMVj2Hjpa4o4YO0rP6XT7ZmSu8waJ4REcv0VpXzYzcFLedF6ES-bnYkX67KVYz3A1VVlLokuzHzkqCXP5JataAf5svcni54Yi7ihHsXZdMB9Qnuhz6ScFUoRliGD3xTfrH9eMcya7N5abNTzV8HtmyKls5jiA3iKKwm2LOW5JFv1BCWsB7wDKhFViWC2OcyZY9fVIF5QvtiV6OBvyQUTmEpPyxoPVNcdKrSr4HqxKDMNKTHYtQeshrJr3TYJrMOUoUyBKBqVjlqxqRxCvAC9nslIpT6CQoEpK1GWHXG1EBemdyGx776PCBSunBoIZRbYUSfaXywsRmhZzHXDQ/b5TUp-5IaH6JQSBkwJxj-IaGI5Dn8tvH/19" style="font-size: inherit; text-decoration: none; color: inherit;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;" valign="top" width="80"&gt;&lt;img alt="零" height="80" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i59VlR9JurHo/v8/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; border-radius: 10px;" width="80" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt;&lt;p style="font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; color: inherit; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;零&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.2; margin: 4px 0 0 0; color: inherit; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;中国和印度发出十年气候警告信号&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;