--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Manuel Velasquez/Getty Images 来自 Getty Images 南美洲&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着罗里·麦克罗伊 (Rory McIlroy) 的&lt;/strong&gt;第二次大师赛胜利被载入奥古斯塔史册，高尔夫界的注意力开始转向 LIV，并有报道称，沙特支持的新贵联盟可能面临&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/2SvvpkItnVLT5QB6tnKBE3qcGDGApQjnSaISHus-qHeD4glk7K_9_eTAbbmWCSj6N2TUNhIR4g4toA4jDnWyUofXGXKW9Djlc-ydAKgRutTNoGGnuICKA7eFJfRDMNYkKFsAf3Fs5Tn8Q3p6tjqz0CunwD8fzKPUF6nrzSsFjWiMI3BBvgsxy_6kNQEccqZTRdJUwSLNH16HEeNWfHT4Ho_srzPRkAad94Qrux76IHz86hXtMFA4Nfs_r-gC8iYXv4R1s_OLOzfO2TIFXioVvDTTT1qV0woY-CDpdIwZPTUDIVs7BUJ1YdnsSgKyI60HQb-niDrhq_OrY-tyXLFSE2xqjBGbubgsWD86QAuEFT9XO7hX1gDd51qrkl1-iRpw1BrUlyORul33FuRV5PxhvILoHCewI9IAk_tnNDBRgZpIDXDlO3542-xMltaPCJ-Q0mOh3lwwtCyBkP9tlNJ2kEyai29GNyS37oR-sVNK6tQldHvduR4sVzrt54MNJz37kO9eDB25DQoMTwMFsVsvnyFXMAiL/MwwxUKuaKRWKWJDg0rpi2tximM6Bhlre/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="沙特阿拉伯称将考虑终止对 LIV Golf 的资助"&gt;失去资金的&lt;/a&gt;风险。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;众所周知，LIV&lt;/strong&gt;一直在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/wM6DSUV6cmUDU90SablkWd-JriFGNjApeqj_ss_PPEMMvnsyCgrdcn1GP4Ot_5GuoR8N8eLhWLtAu73u85PeJK4HFr4DuP4d5NqvCDueEFKA9DWv3pk36xHhkRUd-fzP5BUlG-cdT1zefyKzodP3R_OTT2WtAfTlNfCss86ArYbH45kIKsZmmObYruR1578d6hd4az-jbZBXwqlUFSXxRaENHs3y7t1-TV3te8MnRR5hD_zblOmS4xx9nIKo39AHzWtqvquPuQK54viEwQHVIat4vOApr7nE32sTXkpyE-drubkQzwBNJt_zcaiZmjUgU6ibRk3nbNNZoDtwz8B3pueEOGv16hgk-SBTtEhURU1zPOJPEJBUCNVjg0WlI7prqrC71RylUHb9APDnbAdLkX4Wfd8-oS8SgNDy1hIKxf1Yr5rHe-GiBffpMcfBIlHEMEPs7H7u41mCV5GMk2d_Y_q-hSmHBJg3iVbngyL8zSVFbDDnRwI3AG4hBFxtNOok1YgJfdd1cWSWKqKA8DLfh1XJN9hAH3FYXgWD/0726